TC1: Create an account with MF

step 1: navigate to http://www.matchesfashion.com/
step 2: click sign in button
step 3: create an account (title, fname, lname, email, pword, confirm pword, country, number)
step 4: De-select 'If you would prefer not to receive news and special promotions by email from MATCHESFASHION.COM, please untick the box'
step 5: click Create and account

TC2: Verify account is created and signed in
Pre-condition: Ensure no one is signed into the website (THIS COULD BE STEPS AS WELL, WE NEED TO DECIDE)

step 1: navigate to http://www.matchesfashion.com/
step 2: click sign in button
step 3: input Current Customer (email, pword)
step 4: click Login
step 5: click account name (top left)
step 6: click My account from drop down list